      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a serious project or a parts donor. The engine has developed a persistent knock and exhibits multiple significant oil leaks, while the transmission frequently slips during gear changes. The body shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust spots and paint fading, and the interior requires a complete overhaul. It is currently not in reliable driving condition and will likely need to be towed from its current location.",
