    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s looking for a brand new home! It's in really solid shape and has been so dependable for me over the years. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it still drives like a dream. It\u2019s the perfect ride if you're looking for something reliable and well-loved without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels for yourself. Drop me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. The powertrain maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, with the critical VANOS system recently overhauled and the rod bearings addressed for long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates and Powerflex bushings to eliminate common floor-pan fatigue. Suspension consists of a well-sorted MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup with Bilstein B6 dampers. Minor cosmetic patina consistent with age, but the drivetrain and kinematics are dialed in for peak lateral G-loading and throttle response.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking quality and reliability. The exterior finish presents beautifully, retaining a high gloss across all panels; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood from standard highway driving, the body is straight and free of any significant dings or scratches. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment. The premium upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s entry bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system\u2014operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in top form. It features a complete service history, with the most recent oil and filter change performed just 500 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. With approximately 75% tread remaining on the tires and recent brake pad replacement, this car is ready for the road with no immediate maintenance needs. It is a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that offers a premium driving experience.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which serves as a testament to engineering excellence and consistent care. Demonstrating robust mechanical health and a sophisticated interior profile, this model offers a seamless blend of performance and comfort. It has undergone a thorough professional assessment to ensure it meets our standards for quality and long-term reliability. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber automobile at a highly competitive valuation.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It looks great and runs even better\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-Variable differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recent overhaul of the rear trailing arm bushings and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are exceptional; the rod bearings have been addressed, and a recent valve adjustment ensures the valvetrain operates with factory precision. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car optimized for throttle response and cornering kinematics.",
